Business Brief -- Alcatel Alsthom S.A.:
   French Firm's 1991 Sales
   Rose 11% to $29.2 Million
Revenue from telecommunications, business systems and
cables rose 18% to 109.68 billion francs. Energy and
transportation revenue rose 16% to 25.89 billion francs.
Sales in the electrical engineering sector rose 4.2% to 15.92
billion francs.
   The company said it increased its market share in its
major fields of activities during the year, especially
telecommunications and power generation.